document_data.Notable Goblets & Chalices:
* ''[[Chalice of Amaunator]]'', a [[Netherese]] [[Amaunatori]] relic.
* ''[[Chalice of continual water]]'', a chalice that produced an endless stream of water.<ref>
* ''[[Chalice of Labelas]]'', one of the [[Great Treasures of Evermeet]].
* ''[[Durlag's Goblet]]'', a ''[[curse]]d'' goblet from the depths of [[Durlag's Tower]].
* ''[[Ebony cup of fate]]'', a mind-affecting device.{{Cite card/Spellfire: Master the Magic/Forgotten Realms Chase|8/25}}
* ''[[Goblet of glory]]'', a goblet that produced an effect similar to a ''[[beaker of plentiful potions]]''.<ref>{{Cite dragon/91/Treasure Trove|59}}
* ''[[Hero's chalice]]'', a mug-like vessel.{{Cite card/Spellfire: Master the Magic/Forgotten Realms Chase|9/25}}
* ''[[Lady's Chalice]]'', a [[Mielikkian]] relic.{{Cite web/Legacy of the Green Regent/What is the Green Regent}}
* ''[[Mazewalker chalice]]'', an [[Ubtaoan]] relic.
* ''[[Skull Chalice of Ch'gakare]]'', a relic of [[Omu]].
* ''[[Wine of Eternity]]'', an incapacitation device.{{Cite card/Spellfire: Master the Magic/Forgotten Realms Chase|21/25}}
* The ''[[Wo-ha Ui-jung]]'' of [[Koryo]], a collection of ten chalices.
* ''[[Wyverntongue Chalice]]'', a relic of [[the Nine]].
